trans-unit.source: Defines the contract for the collection used by ASP.NET session state to manage session.
trans-unit.target: Define o contrato para a coleção usada por estado de sessão ASP.NET para gerenciar a sessão.

trans-unit.source: The ISessionStateItemCollection interface defines the collection of session items exposed to application code by the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionStateContainer> class.
trans-unit.target: A interface de ISessionStateItemCollection define a coleção de itens de sessão exposta ao código do aplicativo, a <xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionStateContainer>classe.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionStateContainer>

trans-unit.source: The ASP.NET implementation of the ISessionStateItemCollection interface is the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection> class.
trans-unit.target: A implementação da interface ISessionStateItemCollection do ASP.NET é a <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection>classe.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection>

trans-unit.source: If you create a class derived from the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreProviderBase> class to store session data, you can either use the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection> class to manage the stored objects or implement the ISessionStateItemCollection interface on your own collection manager.
trans-unit.target: Se você criar uma classe derivada do <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreProviderBase>da classe para armazenar dados de sessão, você pode usar o <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection>classe para gerenciar os objetos armazenados ou implementar a interface ISessionStateItemCollection em seu próprio Gerenciador de coleção.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection> </xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreProviderBase>

trans-unit.source: If you implement the ISessionStateItemCollection interface, you must also create a class that inherits the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreProviderBase> class in order to make use of your ISessionStateItemCollection implementation to manage session variables.
trans-unit.target: Se você implementar a interface ISessionStateItemCollection, você também deve criar uma classe que herda de <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreProviderBase>classe para fazer uso de sua implementação ISessionStateItemCollection para gerenciar as variáveis de sessão.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreProviderBase>

trans-unit.source: An ISessionStateItemCollection implementation must also implement the members of the <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> interface.
trans-unit.target: Uma implementação de ISessionStateItemCollection também deve implementar os membros de <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>interface.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection>

trans-unit.source: Removes all values and keys from the session-state collection.
trans-unit.target: Remove todas as chaves e valores da coleção de estado da sessão.

trans-unit.source: In implementing the Clear method, you should set the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.Dirty%2A> property to `true` to indicatethatvalues in the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection> implementation have been modified.
trans-unit.target: Ao implementar o método Clear, você deve definir o <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.Dirty%2A>propriedade `true` para indicatethatvalues no <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection>implementação foi modificada.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection> </xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.Dirty%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether the collection has been marked as changed.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define um valor que indica se a coleção foi marcada como alterada.

trans-unit.source: The Dirty property is used by the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateModule> to determine whether the values in an <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection> implementation have been modified.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade Dirty é usada pelo <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateModule>para determinar se os valores em um <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection>implementação foi modificada.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection> </xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateModule>

trans-unit.source: In implementing the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection> interface, you should initialize the Dirty property as `false` and set the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Dirty%2A> property to `true` in the implementations of the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.Remove%2A>, <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.RemoveAt%2A>, or <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.Clear%2A> methods.
trans-unit.target: Na implementação o <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection>interface, você deve inicializar a propriedade Dirty como `false` e defina o <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Dirty%2A>propriedade `true` em implementações do <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.Remove%2A>, <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.RemoveAt%2A>, ou <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.Clear%2A>métodos.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.Clear%2A> </xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.RemoveAt%2A> </xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.Remove%2A> </xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Dirty%2A> </xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the <xref href="System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection"></xref> contents have been changed; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Se o <xref href="System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection"> </xref> conteúdo forem alterados; caso contrário, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.target: Exclui um item da coleção.

trans-unit.source: In implementing the Remove method, you should set the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.Dirty%2A> property to `true` to indicatevalues in the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection> implementation have been modified.

trans-unit.source: In implementing the RemoveAt method, you should set the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.Dirty%2A> property to `true` to indicatevalues in the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection> implementation have been modified.
trans-unit.target: Ao implementar o método RemoveAt, você deve definir o <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.Dirty%2A>propriedade `true` para indicatevalues no <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection>implementação foi modificada.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection> </xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.Dirty%2A>

trans-unit.source: Your implementation of the RemoveAt method should throw an <xref:System.ArgumentOutOfRangeException> exception if `index` is less than zero or is equal to or greater than <xref:System.Collections.ICollection.Count%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: A implementação do método RemoveAt deve lançar um <xref:System.ArgumentOutOfRangeException>exceção se `index` é menor que zero ou igual a ou maior que <xref:System.Collections.ICollection.Count%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection.Count%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ArgumentOutOfRangeException>
